{"tid":1186364,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我做政府工, 6月9號見","createTime":"2019-06-05T01:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T01:23:22.000Z","uid":44119,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20f9c10224d8fed86216a1eab921e22c3aac0f6b","tid":1186364,"uid":44119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:19:20.000Z","msg":"我做政府工, 叫做係公司入面既最低層, 人工唔算高但都夠我過穩定既生活。<br />\n<br />\n但係大是大非面前, 6月9號係必須要上街。<br />\n<br />\n除咗因為要反惡法之外, 更加因為愛香港。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多做政府工既都會話要返工不了, 因為你地薪高糧準, 跟本冇需要拎穩定既生活去搏。而且一不小心比心點咗相, 都唔知點同老細交代好。<br />\n<br />\n但係若果條例通過咗, 各大財團撒資, 香港經濟一沉不起, 公務員都係可以凍薪架。<br />\n<br />\n而且人生在世, 唔係淨係為咗個人利益咁簡單, 我地有責任為公義發聲, 為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n打政府工既你, 願意放低個人利益, 為香港下一代發聲嗎?<br />\n<br />\n民陣公布遊行安排如下：<br />\n遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點＞高士威道＞禮頓街＞伊榮街＞邊寧頓街＞軒尼詩道西行車路＞金鐘道＞樂禮街＞夏愨道＞添美道＞立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n集合時間：下午2時半<br />\n起步時間：下午3時（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e73e302b94a6eb40ca52b5de5154eec20be4669","tid":1186364,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"Then?<br />\n<br />\nWFC?<br />\n<br />\n六月九日上街既你，以為自己會很黃台仰，結果卻是李東昇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1173007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1173007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e08b4e95dd286a6500346f15b2bc8a85670d15d5","tid":1186364,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e73e302b94a6eb40ca52b5de5154eec20be4669","tid":1186364,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"Then?<br />\n<br />\nWFC?<br />\n<br />\n六月九日上街既你，以為自己會很黃台仰，結果卻是李東昇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1173007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1173007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"I大保安開工無野做 又出嚟吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2193c066f4dc332e70b3f4b5c666fbcaced1c34","tid":1186364,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e73e302b94a6eb40ca52b5de5154eec20be4669","tid":1186364,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"Then?<br />\n<br />\nWFC?<br />\n<br />\n六月九日上街既你，以為自己會很黃台仰，結果卻是李東昇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1173007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1173007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"你拎到張樓契出黎未呀？<br />\n<br />\n無就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a1f3ee0c7c3ad454b672ea75d2e5a8a5b99f5e","tid":1186364,"uid":38576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"其實做唔做政府工，同反唔反政府，無咩衝突，做政府工嘅老細唔係政府，係納稅人，無義務要盲撐呢個垃圾政府"},{"pid":"13e1afeef84b9c8241a6eb4fb735d5224a7eba04","tid":1186364,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"職位夠低其實上街無咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你估自己係AO/ Inspector咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}